 from mobasser vu vlsi ee vill edu bijan mobasseri subject re v four v six v eight v one two vx organization villanova university lines nine we have seen lots of discussion on automobile engine configuration let me ask a similar question from the aviation field you must have seen images of prop planes with all cylinders exposed i have seen up to eight cylinders positioned radially in a circular fashion with the prop at the center of the circle this arrangement always brings up a geometric dilemma how can one crankshaft throw accomodate eight rods or are the pistons displaced but not visible from the outside bijan